The World Bank approved 100-mln-dlr 20-year loan help modernise machine tool industry Shanghai , New China News Agency said .
It quoted World Bank press release Shanghai saying loan would help modernise 18 plant research institute owned Shanghai Machine Tool Works Shanghai Machine Tool Corp import manufacturing technology develop training programme manager engineer .
With five-year grace period , interest rate currently estimated 7.92 pct would variable , said , without indicating would vary .
